casebody.data:
Victoria Elizabeth DUFRESNE, Appellant,
v.
COMMONWEALTH of Virginia, Appellee. Record No. 0281-15-2 Court of Appeals of Virginia. April 24, 2018

In accordance with the mandate of the Supreme Court of Virginia entered on March 22, 2018 and the order of that Court entered on March 1, 2018, the opinion previously rendered by this Court on October 18, 2016 is withdrawn, the mandate entered on that date is vacated, and the judgment of the trial court convicting appellant of grand larceny is affirmed.

This order shall be published and certified to the trial court.
